    <description># Welcome to The Gauntlet Forums

The Gauntlet Forums are a place to discuss Story Games, Indie and OSR tabletop RPGs, and LARPs. If you’d like to join the discussion please:

* Review the [Inclusivity Policy](https://discourse.funtimers.club/t/the-inclusivity-policy/160): The Gauntlet strives to create a safe and inclusive space for all gamers from all walks of life.
* Review the [FAQ](https://discourse.funtimers.club/faq): We’re here for great discussions - quality over quantity.
* Learn about [Trust Levels](https://blog.discourse.org/2018/06/understanding-discourse-trust-levels/): The more active you are, the more active you can become.
* [Note](https://discourse.funtimers.club/t/fyi-a-number-of-email-providers-will-not-accept-mail-from-us-including-yahoo-and-hotmail/414/): Certain email providers are not accepting mail from us.

Done reading? Then hit the Sign Up button!</description>
    
